Pre-Game Insights: Madagascar will scuffle to beat The Gambia to end their winless run in the continent’s biennial biggest football fiesta qualifiers.
The Gambia must defeat Madagascar to maintain their chances of qualifying for the 2025 Africa Cup of Nations.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Madagascar and The Gambia are both with a point each after two qualifier matches.
Tunisia will play against Comoros Islands in the other Group A qualifier match today, Friday, 11th October 2024 in Tunis at 7pm.
Others: The Tunisians currently sit top-spot in Group A of the continent’s biennial biggest football fiesta qualifiers with 6 points after winning their two qualifier matches.
